                          <summary>The second half of a history of the Muslim empires and dynasties by ʻAbd al-Malik ʻIṣāmī</summary>
                                       <msItem xml:id="manuscript_13818-item1"> <author key="person_314790292" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/314790292">
